4 Hetuduka, Saññojanadukādi
Hetuduka, Saññojanadukādi
10.
48Nahetuṃ nosaññojanaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe…  nahetuṃ noganthaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ. Sabbattha nava.)
49Nahetuṃ nooghaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe…  nahetuṃ noyogaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ. Sabbattha nava. Vipākaṃ natthi.)
50Nahetuṃ nonīvaraṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ. Sabbattha nava.)
51Nahetuṃ noparāmāsaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ. Sabbattha nava. Vipākaṃ natthi.)
